\v 4 cˀoa⁴ jme¹-ni³ nca³ tsi² tsa² to⁴jin⁴ coan⁴soa³-si¹ni³na³jin⁴, cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ coaon⁴³ nca³ jon², nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² nˀion¹ nta³ tsa³ˀya³ta³con²-lai²⁴jin⁴. Cˀoa⁴ coan⁴ tsa² cjoa⁴ˀai¹cao⁴-na³ cho⁴ta⁴ macedonios, tsa² scoe⁴-no³ nca³ to⁴jo³ cje³ ti³yo³nta³-jin²nio³.
