\v 1 To⁴nca³ an³ nia¹³ xi³ Pablo vˀe³tsˀoa²³-no³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ntˀe¹ cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ˀi³nta³jin³ta³con² jo³-ni³ tsa² tsˀe⁴ Cristo, an³ xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ na³nqui³ cjia³ cˀia⁴ nca³ ti²jna⁴ nqui³xcon³ nca³ jon², to⁴nca³ cˀia⁴ nca³ xin² ti²jna⁴, ma³nˀion¹-coan³ cao⁴ nca³ jon².
\v 2 Vˀe³tsˀoa²³-no³ nca³ tsi² tsa² tjin¹ne²-na³ nca³ coan⁴nˀion¹jin³coan³ cˀia⁴ nca³ ti²jna⁴jin³-no³, jo³-sˀin² ma³nˀion¹ta³con²coa⁴ cˀa³ xi³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si¹cja³ˀai³tsjen³ xi³ tˀa³tsain⁴-jin⁴ nca³ ti³mai³⁴-jin⁴ jo³-sˀin² me³-le⁴ yao³-na⁴jin⁴.
