\v 5 Ni²qui³xo²yai³⁴-jin⁴ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³ xi³ ncˀa³ tjio¹ cˀoa⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ xi³ ncˀa³ tjin¹, xi³ vi³so¹tjen⁴ co²ntran⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴chji⁴ne⁴-le⁴ Ni³na¹. Ntoa³nˀioin¹⁴-jin⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³, jme¹-ni³ nca³ si⁴²tjo³son²-si¹ni³le⁴ Cristo.
